jobs_results.description:
We are looking for iOS mobile developer for our ecommerce client in Ville St. Laurent.

Skills

. Experience with software development;

. Solid knowledge of OOP programming;

. Have built at least one iPad/iPhone/Android/Tablet application;

. Solid understanding of Cocoa/UIKit frameworks and the iPhone SDK;

. Solid understanding of Android OS and its SDK;

. Proficiency in Xcode 4, Interface Builder and Instruments;

. Proficiency in Eclipse, DDMS;

. Solid understanding of the iPhone/iPad/Android Application development process;

. Experience using version control repositories such as SVN or Git;

. Experience consuming web services (REST) and processing data (XML/JSON);

. Solid understanding of data structure and network protocols;

. A basic understanding of backend components that drive mobile applications

. Interface design skills;

. Strong analytical and communication skills;

. Strong interpersonal skills;

. Innovative and creative personality;

. Independent, yet able to work well within a team.

Our software client in Montreal is looking for intermediate iOS developer to start ASAP.
• 5 years or less as iOS developer;
• Experience with SDK iOS10+, Objective C, Swift 4, CoreData, Storyboard et XCode;
• Comfortable with GIT and agile.
